
I jumped back down to his lap and folded my arms around his neck so tightly that if he was human he would probably be choked to death.
He hugged me, "Is that a yes?"
I nodded, "Yes! Of course it's a yes!"
As we were embracing each other in the sand I head Louis' voice come from the back door, "Well look at that. We missed the proposal because you wanted to argue about my romantic abilities."
"It was your fault!" I laughed at the Irish man trying to defend himself.
Zayn chuckled, "We may be getting more mature but those two sure aren't."
I smiled, "I like our little family. I can't wait to celebrate with them."
Zayn leaned in for another kiss and we laid in the moonlight together to share this special moment.